<title>USA: Steel Technologies completes ACP purchase.</title>
<headline>Steel Technologies completes ACP purchase.</headline>
<dateline>LOUISVILLE, Ky 1997-04-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Steel Technologies Inc said it completed the previously reported acquisition of  Atlantic Coil Processing Inc.</p>
<p>The company purchased all of ACP's stock for about $20 million.</p>
<p>The acquistion added three new facilities in North Carolina to the eight operations run by Steel Technologies in the United States and Mexico.</p>
<p>Steel Technologies and ACP are both steel processing companies.</p>
